WEBVTT

00:00:00.140 --> 00:00:03.060
=The Crow Princess of Fortune=

00:00:03.060 --> 00:00:04.980
=Episode 17=

00:00:05.620 --> 00:00:09.180
I know this isn't right.

00:00:09.340 --> 00:00:10.700
Are you lecturing me?

00:00:11.340 --> 00:00:12.860
I wouldn't dare.

00:00:13.580 --> 00:00:14.700
Hmph.

00:00:14.900 --> 00:00:16.220
You wouldn't dare?

00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:19.220
Your father being foolish is one thing,

00:00:19.340 --> 00:00:22.620
but how can a lucky star like you
be even dumber than a jinx?

00:00:23.940 --> 00:00:27.099
Xiao Suisui is only five, yet she already
knows how to stand up for Father,

00:00:27.100 --> 00:00:29.660
make money, and win people over. But you?

00:00:29.780 --> 00:00:31.740
All you ever say is useless nonsense.

00:00:40.380 --> 00:00:42.220
Come here.

00:00:44.500 --> 00:00:47.619
Everything I'm doing
is for your own good.

00:00:47.620 --> 00:00:49.340
You're the Emperor's grandson.

00:00:49.380 --> 00:00:51.740
One day, you'll inherit the throne.

00:00:51.820 --> 00:00:55.260
If Xiao Heng doesn't die,
your father's position won't be secure.

00:00:55.740 --> 00:00:56.860
Do you understand?

00:01:00.180 --> 00:01:03.020
Chun'er, take him back to the palace.

00:01:03.220 --> 00:01:04.340
Yes.

00:01:15.180 --> 00:01:16.379
The Imperial Preceptor said

00:01:16.380 --> 00:01:19.700
Xiao Heng must pass through Luoyan Slope
this time on his way to Jiacheng Pass.

00:01:20.300 --> 00:01:22.250
The Imperial Preceptor
has already set up a formation there.

00:01:22.250 --> 00:01:23.660
Once Xiao Heng enters,

00:01:23.740 --> 00:01:25.940
he won't make it out alive.

00:01:27.620 --> 00:01:29.659
The Imperial Preceptor
really knows what he's doing, Mother.

00:01:29.660 --> 00:01:30.780
You...

00:01:57.500 --> 00:01:58.939
Little Princess.

00:01:58.940 --> 00:02:01.579
Please stop blowing that thing.

00:02:01.580 --> 00:02:03.299
I'm already hard of hearing.

00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:07.020
If you keep blowing that loudly,
I'll really go deaf.

00:02:08.500 --> 00:02:11.499
Ouch. Tell me, where did Father go?

00:02:11.500 --> 00:02:14.460
Little Princess, please stop asking.

00:02:14.780 --> 00:02:16.019
Before Prince Jing left,

00:02:16.020 --> 00:02:17.299
he specifically told us

00:02:17.300 --> 00:02:20.300
not to let you know about this.

00:02:20.860 --> 00:02:23.579
Everything Prince Jing did
was for your own good.

00:02:23.580 --> 00:02:24.620
Hmph.

00:02:28.100 --> 00:02:29.220
Ouch.

00:02:29.500 --> 00:02:30.700
What are you doing?

00:02:30.820 --> 00:02:31.780
Uncle Shiwan.

00:02:31.860 --> 00:02:32.499
Ah.

00:02:32.500 --> 00:02:36.739
You've hidden quite a lot
of silver notes under your pillow.

00:02:36.740 --> 00:02:37.699
This...

00:02:37.700 --> 00:02:39.219
What are you trying to say?

00:02:39.220 --> 00:02:41.099
Oh dear.

00:02:41.100 --> 00:02:44.460
My little pouch feels so empty.

00:02:44.500 --> 00:02:47.220
Shouldn't it get fed a little?

00:02:47.380 --> 00:02:48.139
Little Princess,

00:02:48.140 --> 00:02:51.579
please don't get
any ideas about this money.

00:02:51.580 --> 00:02:54.299
I've been saving it for over ten years.

00:02:54.300 --> 00:02:55.979
This is my retirement money.

00:02:55.980 --> 00:02:57.779
Please don't...

00:02:57.780 --> 00:03:00.199
And on your ceiling beam too.

00:03:00.200 --> 00:03:02.100
Quite the treasure stash
you've got there.

00:03:02.380 --> 00:03:04.899
But that spot isn't very safe.

00:03:04.900 --> 00:03:07.819
What if an eagle
snatches it away someday?

00:03:07.820 --> 00:03:10.139
What do you mean
an eagle snatching it away?

00:03:10.140 --> 00:03:11.499
Ahahaha.

00:03:11.500 --> 00:03:13.219
Little Princess,
now that you mention it,

00:03:13.220 --> 00:03:14.699
I suddenly remembered everything.

00:03:14.700 --> 00:03:15.579
Hahaha.

00:03:15.580 --> 00:03:18.780
Prince Jing left early this morning.

00:03:19.220 --> 00:03:20.899
I heard he took the official road.

00:03:20.900 --> 00:03:22.499
He should arrive

00:03:22.500 --> 00:03:25.420
at the government office
near Luoyan Slope before dark.

00:03:26.100 --> 00:03:28.739
A wise man knows when to yield.

00:03:28.740 --> 00:03:29.539
Ouch...

00:03:29.540 --> 00:03:30.780
Don't worry.

00:03:30.940 --> 00:03:33.739
I'm not interested
in your little savings.

00:03:33.740 --> 00:03:35.940
Ouch. That's great.

00:03:36.020 --> 00:03:39.219
Come on. Let's go find Father.

00:03:39.220 --> 00:03:40.940
Yes. I'll go pack right away.

00:03:41.580 --> 00:03:43.620
Suisui, something bad happened!

00:03:44.100 --> 00:03:44.900
Suisui!

00:03:45.100 --> 00:03:46.339
Suisui, your father...

00:03:46.340 --> 00:03:47.700
What happened to Father?

00:03:47.740 --> 00:03:49.179
What happened to Prince Jing?

00:03:49.180 --> 00:03:51.499
There's an ambush at Luoyan Slope.

00:03:51.500 --> 00:03:53.739
The Imperial Preceptor
set up a formation there.

00:03:53.740 --> 00:03:55.299
If your father walks into it,

00:03:55.300 --> 00:03:56.939
he won't make it back out.

00:03:56.940 --> 00:04:00.420
- Uncle Shiwan. Prepare the horses.
- Yes. Prepare the horses! Go!

00:04:00.580 --> 00:04:02.220
Be careful!

00:04:03.600 --> 00:04:06.680
(County Office)

00:04:08.900 --> 00:04:09.900
This way, please.

00:04:14.540 --> 00:04:15.579
Your Highness.

00:04:15.580 --> 00:04:17.620
The heavy rain ahead
washed out the official road.

00:04:17.620 --> 00:04:19.499
I'm afraid you won't
be able to continue tonight.

00:04:19.500 --> 00:04:21.220
We've already
prepared a guest room for you.

00:04:22.340 --> 00:04:24.699
Please rest here for the night.

00:04:24.700 --> 00:04:26.560
Would it be alright
to continue tomorrow morning?

00:04:28.380 --> 00:04:29.620
Thank you for the trouble.

00:04:31.900 --> 00:04:33.219
You should all get some rest too.

00:04:33.220 --> 00:04:34.180
Yes.

00:04:47.660 --> 00:04:48.339
Father.

00:04:48.340 --> 00:04:49.299
Father, where are you?

00:04:49.300 --> 00:04:50.699
I'm scared.

00:04:50.700 --> 00:04:51.820
Suisui?

00:04:51.940 --> 00:04:53.500
That's Suisui's voice.

00:04:53.740 --> 00:04:55.299
Could Dajun have failed to stop her?

00:04:55.300 --> 00:04:57.499
Father, come save me!

00:04:57.500 --> 00:04:59.260
Don't be afraid, Suisui. Father's here.

00:05:06.880 --> 00:05:10.199
♪Little lucky star,
twinkling with a wink at me♪

00:05:10.200 --> 00:05:14.039
♪Every Chinese New Year day brings
the luckiest fortune slip♪

00:05:14.040 --> 00:05:17.559
♪The God of Wealth favors me,
the Matchmaker ties red strings for me♪

00:05:17.560 --> 00:05:20.520
♪With firecrackers going off,
good things keep coming one after another♪

00:05:21.400 --> 00:05:25.039
♪Make a wish on the very first day
of the Chinese New Year♪

00:05:25.040 --> 00:05:28.800
♪By the second day,
my belly's already round♪

00:05:28.880 --> 00:05:32.199
♪Always talking about dieting,
but the chub never disappears♪

00:05:32.200 --> 00:05:36.240
♪Good food brings joy
and happiness every single day♪

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:45.519
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
every year is filled with joy♪

00:05:45.520 --> 00:05:49.159
♪I'm bringing blessings to everyone♪

00:05:49.160 --> 00:05:52.879
♪Hands clasped together in greeting♪

00:05:52.880 --> 00:05:56.519
♪May every family be sweet and happy♪

00:05:56.520 --> 00:06:00.199
♪With lucky stars shining bright,
may everything go your way♪

00:06:00.200 --> 00:06:02.119
♪Endlessly flowing♪

00:06:02.120 --> 00:06:08.320
♪Good fortune♪